text: Kuvykovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Akhmetovsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 294 as of 2010. There are 9 streets. == Geography == It is located 28 km from Kushnarenkovo, 27 km from Akhmetovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Kuvykovo
